{"tid":112863,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實國際特赦組織嘅作用係邊？","createTime":"2017-02-08T13:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T00:11:36.000Z","uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a388307d4e8b914140bb5af6afa0ac11e2ef4494","tid":112863,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"我由細到大都唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話自己目的係防止侵害人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好似敘利亞單野<br />\n佢爆完之後敘利亞當局人一樣照殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢鬧完美國佬關塔那摩佢唔會關閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁既然佢都唔會比到壓力人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個ngo作用係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b105da9146d3c8dededd7db162c3fd511319c9","tid":112863,"uid":19010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:30:49.000Z","msg":"呃錢用<br />\n籌款籌款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eaea95334f34a785154a0a82b713549192d88ca","tid":112863,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:45:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ec6afdb590e7484202672f12943b5595fac4749b","tid":112863,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:46:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際特赦組織一執笠<br />\n即刻大批廢柒左膠失業搵唔到工做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實ngo最廢應該係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a18387a3b00e0c466702a6dbe94e6fcadb09475f","tid":112863,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T13:47:06.000Z","msg":"你咁講所有國際組織都係廢㗎啦<img src=